quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,68,"Mi…óo yottina e mo'on Nule Joomi am, min (non) ko mi laa…ďanoo on (reedu), koolnii…óo."
  7,69,"E kaawo fii waajo no ari on immorde ka Joomi mon e dow gorko jeyaa…óo e mo'on, fii yo o jeertin on?! ciftoree tuma nde O wa…ónoo on lomtii…ďe …ďaawo yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen, O …ďeydi on ka tagoore semmbe. ciftoree dokke Alla …óe mbelejo'o, on malete."
  7,70,"∆Āe mbi'i : "E a ar e amen fii yo min ndew Alla tan, min ngacca kon ko baabiraa…ďe amen …ďeen ndewatnoo?! Awa addan amen ko podan…óaa men kon (e lepte) si tawii ko a jeyaa…óo e gooŇčnu…ďe …ďeen."
  7,71,"O maaki : "GooŇč…óii yanii e mon immorde ka Joomi mon so…ďe (lepte) e tikkere. E on mbee√Īdat e am fii in…óe …óe innu…óon onon e baabiraa…ďe mo'on, Alla Jippinaali fii majje hujja?! padee! min, won dude e mo'on, ko mi jeyaa…óo e fat…ďe …ďen"."
  7,72,"Min nda…óniri mo e …ďeen won du…ďe e makko yurmeende amen, men ta∆īi …ďabbe …ďeen yeddu…ďe Aayeeje amen …óeen, …ďe laatanooki gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  7,73,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e Samuuda'en, musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on Saalihu, o maaki : "Eehey mon yim…ďe am, ndewee Alla. dewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori mo. GooŇč…óii arii on …ďanngannduyee immorde ka Joomi mon : mbaa ko ngeelooba Alla ma'ande wonan de on, tertee mba √Īaama ka leydi Alla, wata on memir ba bone sakko lepte muusu…óe nannga on"."